				>
			</p>
			<ul
				role="list"
				class="col-span-2 col-start-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-4 text-xs leading-none"
			>
				<li>
					<span>
						Built an interactive web tool for generating artistic patterns from
						a mathematical concept
					</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<span>
						Implemented dynamic pattern generation, SVG and PNG downloads, and
						generation logic with full unit tests
					</span>
