				role="list"
				class="col-span-2 col-start-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-4 text-xs leading-none"
			>
				<li>
					<span>
						Designed and developed an accessible, extensible, Shadcn-compatible
						UI component available as an npm package
					</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<span> Designed and implemented smooth animation using Motion </span>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="col-span-4 col-start-1 mt-12 grid grid-cols-subgrid">
			<h3 class="col-start-3 text-sm leading-none font-semibold uppercase">
				Neural network for solving Schrödinger equation
			</h3>
			<p class="col-start-4 text-right text-sm">Senior project</p>
			<ul
				role="list"
				class="col-span-2 col-start-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-4 text-xs leading-none"
			>
				<li>
					<span>
						Built and trained an unsupervised, physics-informed neural network
						for solving the Schrödinger equation in 1D quantum wells using
						Python and TensorFlow
					</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<span
						>Model predicted energy values within 0.5% and probability
						distribution within 10% error range, significantly improving on
						prior literatures
					</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>
